data.description: This charming generous sized 3 bedroom, 2 full bathrooms/1 half bath, split-level condominium is a delight. This home features a partial open floor plan and in unit washer/dryer hookups. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom. At the end of a long day step out onto your patio to enjoy your favorite beverage. Step inside to discover the home for you!       Come experience space, functionality and charm. First time homebuyers do not miss this opportunity. Nearby shopping, dining, entertainment and schools. This inviting condo awaits you but will not last long!  Submit your offer today!  Will be open for showings: Jan. 27 & 28th 10:00 am - 2:00 pm.
